.TH "set_update_marker" 9 "set_update_marker" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
set_update_marker \- set update marker.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" set_update_marker
.BI "(struct ubi_device *ubi "  ","
.BI "struct ubi_volume *vol "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ubi" 12
UBI device description object
.IP "vol" 12
volume description object
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function sets the update marker flag for volume \fIvol\fP. Returns zero
in case of success and a negative error code in case of failure.
